{"id":168425,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/新浪微博：（温州动车事故）上面给央媒下达的追/","date":"2011-07-24T09:24:24Z","modified":"2011-07-24T18:38:31Z","title":"新浪微博：（温州动车事故）上面给央媒下达的追加指示","content":"<p><span style=\"color: #7f9140;line-height: 20px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 12px\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/2266040701\">@良知1111</a>：<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E7%8E%8B%E5%88%A9%E8%8A%AC\">@王利芬</a><a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E8%96%9B%E8%9B%AE%E5%AD%90\">@薛蛮子</a><a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E6%9D%8E%E6%89%BF%E9%B9%8F\">@李承鹏</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%8E%E5%BB%BA%E5%B5%98\">@于建嵘</a><a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E8%96%9B%E6%B6%8C%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A\">@薛涌微博</a>。今天上午上面给央媒下达的追加指示：「对温州事故报道的最新要求：1、死伤数字以权威部门发布为准；2、报道频度不要太密；3、要多报道感人事迹，如义务献血和出租车司机不收钱等等；4、对事故原因不要挖掘，以权威部门的发布为准；5、不要做反思和评论。」<span class=\"source_att MIB_linkbl\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 18px\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/2266040701/xgdqtEOlu\"><strong>原文转发</strong><strong>(7771)</strong></a><span class=\"MIB_line_l\" style=\"color: #d6d6d6;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 9px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 8px\">|</span><a href=\"http://weibo.com/2266040701/xgdqtEOlu\"><strong>原文评论</strong><strong>(1748)</strong></a></span></span></p>\n","author":964,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9034,8859,10009,16285,17358,10675]}